类 PrimitiveValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.real_logic.sbe.PrimitiveValue

  • public class PrimitiveValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to encapsulate values for primitives. Used for nullValue, minValue, maxValue, and constants
